# R sandbox base image CVEs (debian:bookworm-slim)
# Debian-managed OS packages. Fixes require Debian to publish updates to bookworm.
# Sandbox Lambdas are VPC-isolated with no internet access and no IAM credentials.

# zlib1g heap buffer overflow in MiniZip. Sandbox R code has no zip extraction.
CVE-2023-45853

# libsystemd0 - pulled in as transitive dep. No systemd services in the container.
CVE-2026-29111

# libexpat1 XML parser. Sandbox R code does not parse XML via libexpat.
CVE-2026-25210

# libc-bin (glibc) - core C library, cannot be removed. Awaiting Debian patch.
CVE-2026-0861

# libtinfo6 (ncurses) - terminal handling. Sandbox runs non-interactively.
CVE-2025-69720

# libtiff6 DoS. Sandbox R code does not process TIFF images.
CVE-2023-52355

# libldap-2.5-0 NULL deref. Sandbox has no LDAP connections.
CVE-2023-2953

# libharfbuzz0b text shaping. Pulled in by R's graphics stack.
# Requires crafted font files to exploit.
CVE-2023-25193

# xdg-utils URI validation bypass. No desktop environment in the container.
CVE-2022-4055

# r-cran-jsonlite (native yajl C parser)
# CVE-2022-24795: integer overflow requires >2GB JSON input (sandbox limits to 1MB)
# CVE-2017-16516: buffer over-read in yajl parser
CVE-2022-24795
CVE-2017-16516
